 become pretty important over time, which was always the goal.\", \"from\": 623, \"to\": 695, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 663, \"to\": 667}, {\"ngram\": \"the goal\", \"from\": 686, \"to\": 694}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And those who have been involved say it is far more meaningful than they could have ever imagined going in.\", \"from\": 696, \"to\": 803, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"With that as the backdrop, golf is set to be played for the third time this week in the Olympic Golf Tournament to be conducted at Le Golf National outside of Paris.\", \"from\": 805, \"to\": 970, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 964, \"end\": 969, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.5682257383480255e-14, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the backdrop\", \"from\": 818, \"to\": 830}, {\"ngram\": \"golf\", \"from\": 832, \"to\": 836}, {\"ngram\": \"the third time\", \"from\": 861, \"to\": 875}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Golf Tournament\", \"from\": 889, \"to\": 916}, {\"ngram\": \"Le Golf National\", \"from\": 936, \"to\": 952}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The one-time home to the DP World Tour\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s French Open and the 2018 Ryder Cup won by Europe, it will see a good field with the likes of two-time major winner Schauffele, No.\", \"from\": 972, \"to\": 1145, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the DP World\", \"from\": 993, \"to\": 1005}, {\"ngram\": \"Tour\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 1006, \"to\": 1014}, {\"ngram\": \"French Open\", \"from\": 1015, \"to\": 1026}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2018 Ryder Cup\", \"from\": 1031, \"to\": 1049}, {\"ngram\": \"Europe\", \"from\": 1057, \"to\": 1063}, {\"ngram\": \"a good field\", \"from\": 1077, \"to\": 1089}, {\"ngram\": \"the likes\", \"from\": 1095, \"to\": 1104}, {\"ngram\"