resource/Matt_Fitzpatrick\"}, {\"begin\": 1247, \"end\": 1261, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Viktor_Hovland\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Viktor Hovland\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13156709\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Viktor_Hovland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Viktor_Hovland\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"1-ranked Scottie Scheffler\", \"from\": 1146, \"to\": 1172}, {\"ngram\": \"plenty\", \"from\": 1266, \"to\": 1272}, {\"ngram\": \"others\", \"from\": 1276, \"to\": 1282}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While the entire field might not be the strongest, lest we forget a couple of players outside of the top 100 in the Official World Golf Ranking finished second and third to Schauffele in Tokyo\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094Rory Sabbatini and C.T.\", \"from\": 1285, \"to\": 1503, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1480, \"end\": 1494, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rory_Sabbatini\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rory Sabbatini\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13156709\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rory_Sabbatini\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rory_Sabbatini\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the entire field\", \"from\": 1291, \"to\": 1307}, {\"ngram\": \"a couple\", \"from\": 1351, \"to\": 1359}, {\"ngram\": \"players\", \"from\": 1363, \"to\": 1370}, {\"ngram\": \"the top\", \"from\": 1382, \"to\": 1389}, {\"ngram\": \"the Official World Golf Ranking\", \"from\": 1397, \"to\": 1428}, {\"ngram\": \"Schauffele\", \"from\": 1458, \"to\": 1468}, {\"ngram\": \"C.T.\", \"from\": 1499, \"to\": 1503}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Pan, who claimed bronze in a playoff over six others, including McIlroy.\", \"from\": 1504, \"to\": 1576, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Pan\", \"from\": 1504, \"to\": 1507}, {\"ngram\": \"bronze\", \"from\": 1521, \"to\": 1527}, {\"ngram\": \"a playoff\", \"from\": 1531, \"to\": 1540}, {\"ngram\": \"six others\", \"from\": 1546, \"to\": 1556}, {\"ngram\": \"McIlroy\", \"from\": 1568, \"to\": 1575}]}, {\"sentence\": \"McIlroy was among several players\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094Jordan Spieth, Dustin Johnson and Jason Day among them\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094who skipped the Rio games over various levels of indifference.\", \"from\": 1578, \"to\": 1733, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1614, \"end\": 1627, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Spieth\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jordan Spieth\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13156709\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Spieth\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Spieth\"}, {\"begin\": 1629, \"end\": 1643, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dustin_Johnson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Dustin Johnson\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dustin_Johnson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dustin_Johnson\"}, {\"begin\": 1648, \"end\": 1657, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jason_Day\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.899366335312479e-113, \"text\": \"Jason Day\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13156709\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jason_Day\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jason_Day\"}, {\"begin\": 1687, \"end\": 1690, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.999987421633687, \"rank\": 1.2578524174837638e-05, \"text\": \"Rio\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"McIlroy\", \"from\": 1578, \"to\": 1585}, {\"ngram\": \"them\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094who\", \"from\": 1664, \"to\": 1674}, {\"ngram\": \"various levels\", \"from\": 1702, \"to\": 1716}, {\"ngram\": \"indifference\", \"from\": 1720, \"to\": 1732}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI made some comments before that were probably uneducated and impulsive, but coming here and experiencing it, seeing, feeling everything that goes on not just Olympic golf but just the Olympics in general, that sort of Olympic spirit\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s definitely bitten me,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d McIlroy said in Tokyo.\", \"from\": 1735, \"to\": 2023, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2017, \"end\": 2022, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9794534689617749, \"rank\": 0.02097754685323844, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI\", \"from\": 1735, \"to\": 1739}, {\"ngram\": \"some comments\", \"from\": 1745, \"to\": 1758}, {\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 1864, \"to\": 1874}, {\"ngram\": \"not just Olympic golf\", \"from\": 1888, \"to\": 1909}, {\"ngram\": \"just the Olympics\", \"from\": 1914, \"to\": 1931}, {\"ngram\": \"that sort\", \"from\": 1944, \"to\": 1953}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic\", \"from\": 1957, \"to\": 1964}, {\"ngram\": \"spirit\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 1965, \"to\": 1975}, {\"ngram\": \"McIlroy\", \"from\": 2001, \"to\": 2008}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099m excited how this week\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s turned out and excited for the future.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d McIlroy shot 67 in the final round three years ago to finish two shots back of Schauffele and one behind Sabbatini and in that seven-way tie for third that took a four-hole playoff to decide.\", \"from\": 2024, \"to\": 2293, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099m\", \"from\": 2024, \"to\": 2032}, {\"ngram\": \"week\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 2050, \"to\": 2058}, {\"ngram\": \"the future.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d McIlroy\", \"from\": 2086, \"to\": 2108}, {\"ngram\": \"the final round\", \"from\": 2120, \"to\": 2135}, {\"ngram\": \"two shots\", \"from\": 2162, \"to\": 2171}, {\"ngram\": \"Schauffele\", \"from\": 2180, \"to\": 2190}, {\"ngram\": \"Sabbatini\", \"from\": 2206, \"to\": 2215}, {\"ngram\": \"that seven-way tie\", \"from\": 2223, \"to\": 2241}, {\"ngram\": \"a four-hole playoff\", \"from\": 2262, \"to\": 2281}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He was eliminated on the third extra hole.\", \"from\": 2294, \"to\": 2336, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the third extra hole\", \"from\": 2315, \"to\": 2335}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI never tried so hard in my life to finish third,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d McIlroy said.\", \"from\": 2338, \"to\": 2407, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my life\", \"from\": 2366, \"to\": 2373}, {\"ngram\": \"McIlroy\", \"from\": 2394, \"to\": 2401}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cIt makes me even more determined going to Paris and trying to pick up one up.\", \"from\": 2408, \"to\": 2488, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2453, \"end\": 2458, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.5682257383480255e-14, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cIt\", \"from\": 2408, \"to\": 2413}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s disappointing going away from here without any hardware.\", \"from\": 2489, \"to\": 2552, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"any hardware\", \"from\": 2539, \"to\": 2551}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cIt\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s been a great experience.\", \"from\": 2554, \"to\": 2588, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a great experience\", \"from\": 2569, \"to\": 2587}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Today was a great day to be up there in contention for a medal, certainly had a different feeling to it than I expected and as I said, I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099m already looking forward (to this year\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s Olympics) and trying to go at least one better but hopefully three better.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d McIlroy is being joined by Irish teammate Shane Lowry, who took part in the opening ceremonies Friday.\", \"from\": 2589, \"to\": 2953, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2878, \"end\": 2883, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland\", \"score\": 0.6179206997624842, \"rank\": 0.6181433279010078, \"text\": \"Irish\", \"types\": [\"Q23442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland\"}, {\"begin\": 2893, \"end\": 2904, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shane_Lowry_(golfer)\", \"score\": 0.9805012734844502, \"rank\": 0.0198863636363513, \"text\": \"Shane Lowry\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13156709\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shane_Lowry_(golfer)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shane_Lowry_(golfer)\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Today\", \"from\": 2589, \"to\": 2594}, {\"ngram\": \"a great day\", \"from\": 2599, \"to\": 2610}, {\"ngram\": \"contention\", \"from\": 2629, \"to\": 2639}, {\"ngram\": \"a medal\", \"from\": 2644, \"to\": 2651}, {\"ngram\": \"a different feeling\", \"from\": 2667, \"to\": 2686}, {\"ngram\": \"I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099m\", \"from\": 2724, \"to\": 2729}, {\"ngram\": \"this year\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s Olympics\", \"from\": 2758, \"to\": 2780}, {\"ngram\": \"three better.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d McIlroy\", \"from\": 2833, \"to\": 2857}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 2914, \"to\": 2918}, {\"ngram\": \"the opening ceremonies\", \"from\": 2922, \"to\": 2944}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Paul Casey was among those who tied for seventh three years ago.\", \"from\": 2955, \"to\": 3019, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2955, \"end\": 2965, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paul_Casey\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.8487065333214644e-113, \"text\": \"Paul Casey\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13156709\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paul_Casey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paul_Casey\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And the result still stings for the Englishman, who now plays for LIV Golf.\", \"from\": 3020, \"to\": 3095, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3086, \"end\": 3094, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LIV_Golf\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"LIV Golf\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LIV_Golf\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LIV_Golf\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the result\", \"from\": 3024, \"to\": 3034}, {\"ngram\": \"the Englishman\", \"from\": 3052, \"to\": 3066}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cTo finish at the time tied third and then walk away from the Olympics with nothing is pretty sobering,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Casey said.\", \"from\": 3097, \"to\": 3217, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3206, \"end\": 3211, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Casey_Demons\", \"score\": 0.9999763272463384, \"rank\": 2.36252431621354e-05, \"text\": \"Casey\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Casey_Demons\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Casey_Demons\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cTo finish\", \"from\": 3097, \"to\": 3109}, {\"ngram\": \"the time\", \"from\": 3113, \"to\": 3121}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 3157, \"to\": 3169}, {\"ngram\": \"nothing\", \"from\": 3175, \"to\": 3182}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cBut it gave me an understanding of what it's like for Olympic athletes to sort of have something that you have worked so hard for, in our case, four years, and then sometimes your Olympic experience is quite humbling.\", \"from\": 3218, \"to\": 3438, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an understanding\", \"from\": 3236, \"to\": 3252}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic athletes\", \"from\": 3275, \"to\": 3291}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 3308, \"to\": 3317}, {\"ngram\": \"our case\", \"from\": 3355, \"to\": 3363}, {\"ngram\": \"your Olympic experience\", \"from\": 3396, \"to\": 3419}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cIn our sport, obviously very different, we play almost week in and week out.\", \"from\": 3440, \"to\": 3519, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our sport\", \"from\": 3446, \"to\": 3455}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On the bright side, I have never been a part of anything like that, to represent your country at any level, and I have done it at an amateur level right through to professional.\", \"from\": 3520, \"to\": 3697, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the bright side\", \"from\": 3523, \"to\": 3538}, {\"ngram\": \"a part\", \"from\": 3558, \"to\": 3564}, {\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 3568, \"to\": 3576}, {\"ngram\": \"your country\", \"from\": 3601, \"to\": 3613}, {\"ngram\": \"any level\", \"from\": 3617, \"to\": 3626}, {\"ngram\": \"an amateur level\", \"from\": 3650, \"to\": 3666}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Olympics ranks right up there as one of the greatest things I have ever done, taking the results out of that.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d And therein lies part of the beauty of golf in the Olympics.\", \"from\": 3698, \"to\": 3876, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Olympics\", \"from\": 3698, \"to\": 3710}, {\"ngram\": \"the greatest things\", \"from\": 3742, \"to\": 3761}, {\"ngram\": \"the results\", \"from\": 3787, \"to\": 3798}, {\"ngram\": \"that.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d\", \"from\": 3806, \"to\": 3814}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 3832, \"to\": 3836}, {\"ngram\": \"the beauty\", \"from\": 3840, \"to\": 3850}, {\"ngram\": \"golf\", \"from\": 3854, \"to\": 3858}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 3862, \"to\": 3874}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It might not be the same as winning a major championship, but it is meaningful, nonetheless, and promises to get more so as time goes on.\", \"from\": 3877, \"to\": 4014, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a major championship\", \"from\": 3913, \"to\": 3933}, {\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 4001, \"to\": 4005}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When you hear that trite phrase \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cgrowing the game,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d the Olympics is actually a way to do that in golf.\", \"from\": 4016, \"to\": 4122, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that trite phrase\", \"from\": 4030, \"to\": 4047}, {\"ngram\": \"the game\", \"from\": 4059, \"to\": 4067}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 4072, \"to\": 4084}, {\"ngram\": \"a way\", \"from\": 4097, \"to\": 4102}, {\"ngram\": \"golf\", \"from\": 4117, \"to\": 4121}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It might not inspire golfers in big golf countries such as the United States, but smaller countries who devote funding to Olympic athletes are now doing so to develop golfers who can be Olympians.\", \"from\": 4123, \"to\": 4319, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4186, \"end\": 4199, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999990738774355, \"rank\": 8.986226928149093e-07, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"golfers\", \"from\": 4144, \"to\": 4151}, {\"ngram\": \"big golf countries\", \"from\": 4155, \"to\": 4173}, {\"ngram\": \"smaller countries\", \"from\": 4205, \"to\": 4222}, {\"ngram\": \"funding\", \"from\": 4234, \"to\": 4241}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic athletes\", \"from\": 4245, \"to\": 4261}, {\"ngram\": \"golfers\", \"from\": 4290, \"to\": 4297}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympians\", \"from\": 4309, \"to\": 4318}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Perhaps that will take another cycle or two of Games to see that kind of impact, but it is quite likely coming.\", \"from\": 4321, \"to\": 4432, \"entities\": [], \"noun_ph