405, \"end\": 6413, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Watkins_Glen_International\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.721622780623241e-38, \"text\": \"The Glen\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Watkins_Glen_International\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Watkins_Glen_International\"}, {\"begin\": 6443, \"end\": 6456, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/North_Berwick\", \"score\": 0.9999999999890861, \"rank\": 1.0938119564499638e-11, \"text\": \"North Berwick\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/North_Berwick\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/North_Berwick\"}, {\"begin\": 6487, \"end\": 6495, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spyglass_Media_Group\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.2107338305451556e-22, \"text\": \"Spyglass\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spyglass_Media_Group\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spyglass_Media_Group\"}, {\"begin\": 6527, \"end\": 6539, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pebble_Beach_Golf_Links\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.70748121086755e-53, \"text\": \"Pebble Beach\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pebble_Beach_Golf_Links\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pebble_Beach_Golf_Links\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cother\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d course\", \"from\": 6417, \"to\": 6439}, {\"ngram\": \"the \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cother\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d course\", \"from\": 6499, \"to\": 6521}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Not as well-known, The Glen has been also referred to as North Berwick\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s East Links.\", \"from\": 6541, \"to\": 6627, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6560, \"end\": 6568, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Watkins_Glen_International\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.721622780623241e-38, \"text\": \"The Glen\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Watkins_Glen_International\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Watkins_Glen_International\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"North Berwick\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 6598, \"to\": 6615}, {\"ngram\": \"East Links\", \"from\": 6616, \"to\": 6626}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The bottom line is you can\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t go wrong with any of them.\", \"from\": 6629, \"to\": 6686, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The bottom line\", \"from\": 6629, \"to\": 6644}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Four of those rounds were over a five-day span in the past week while \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cpreparing\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d for the Olympic golf this week in France.\", \"from\": 6688, \"to\": 6815, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6808, \"end\": 6814, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.8744593729966194, \"rank\": 0.14122070168124018, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"those rounds\", \"from\": 6696, \"to\": 6708}, {\"ngram\": \"a five-day span\", \"from\": 6719, \"to\": 6734}, {\"ngram\": \"the past week\", \"from\": 6738, \"to\": 6751}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic golf\", \"from\": 6778, \"to\": 6794}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cLinks\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d is often a term used generically to describe a golf course\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094and it is done so incorrectly.\", \"from\": 6817, \"to\": 6920, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cLinks\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d\", \"from\": 6817, \"to\": 6828}, {\"ngram\": \"a term\", \"from\": 6838, \"to\": 6844}, {\"ngram\": \"a golf course\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094and\", \"from\": 6874, \"to\": 6893}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009clinks\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d is not interchangeable with any course.\", \"from\": 6921, \"to\": 6974, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009clinks\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d\", \"from\": 6921, \"to\": 6934}, {\"ngram\": \"any course\", \"from\": 6963, \"to\": 6973}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There are various definitions, sometimes not easily explained, butGolf Digest\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s description is simple: \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cA course on oceanside sand dunes that were formed by a receding sea and covered by fertile soil from a river estuary.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d So here\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s the thing about links golf: the ground is your friend!\", \"from\": 6975, \"to\": 7271, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"various definitions\", \"from\": 6985, \"to\": 7004}, {\"ngram\": \"butGolf Digest\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s description\", \"from\": 7038, \"to\": 7068}, {\"ngram\": \"oceanside sand dunes\", \"from\": 7095, \"to\": 7115}, {\"ngram\": \"a receding sea\", \"from\": 7136, \"to\": 7150}, {\"ngram\": \"fertile soil\", \"from\": 7166, \"to\": 7178}, {\"ngram\": \"a river estuary.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d\", \"from\": 7184, \"to\": 7203}, {\"ngram\": \"the thing\", \"from\": 7216, \"to\": 7225}, {\"ngram\": \"links\", \"from\": 7232, \"to\": 7237}, {\"ngram\": \"golf\", \"from\": 7238, \"to\": 7242}, {\"ngram\": \"the ground\", \"from\": 7244, \"to\": 7254}, {\"ngram\": \"your friend\", \"from\": 7258, \"to\": 7269}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For those who can\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t always carry the ball the prescribed distance, it\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s nice to see a shot that is hit short bounce up onto the green or into the vicinity.\", \"from\": 7272, \"to\": 7431, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the ball\", \"from\": 7307, \"to\": 7315}, {\"ngram\": \"the prescribed distance\", \"from\": 7316, \"to\": 7339}, {\"ngram\": \"it\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 7341, \"to\": 7347}, {\"ngram\": \"a shot\", \"from\": 7360, \"to\": 7366}, {\"ngram\": \"short bounce\", \"from\": 7379, \"to\": 7391}, {\"ngram\": \"the green\", \"from\": 7400, \"to\": 7409}, {\"ngram\": \"the vicinity\", \"from\": 7418, \"to\": 7430}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In fact, that is what gives you an appreciation of what someone like Schauffele managed to do at Royal Troon.\", \"from\": 7433, \"to\": 7542, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7530, \"end\": 7541, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Royal_Troon_Golf_Club\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Royal Troon\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Royal_Troon_Golf_Club\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Royal_Troon_Golf_Club\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"fact\", \"from\": 7436, \"to\": 7440}, {\"ngram\": \"an appreciation\", \"from\": 7465, \"to\": 7480}, {\"ngram\": \"someone\", \"from\": 7489, \"to\": 7496}, {\"ngram\": \"Schauffele\", \"from\": 7502, \"to\": 7512}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At the highest level, golf is such an exact game.\", \"from\": 7543, \"to\": 7592, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the highest level\", \"from\": 7546, \"to\": 7563}, {\"ngram\": \"golf\", \"from\": 7565, \"to\": 7569}, {\"ngram\": \"such an exact game\", \"from\": 7573, \"to\": 7591}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Players know how far they hit their irons within a yard or two.\", \"from\": 7593, \"to\": 7656, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Players\", \"from\": 7593, \"to\": 7600}, {\"ngram\": \"their irons\", \"from\": 7623, \"to\": 7634}, {\"ngram\": \"a yard\", \"from\": 7642, \"to\": 7648}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And that\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s what makes links golf so intriguing.\", \"from\": 7657, \"to\": 7706, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"links\", \"from\": 7681, \"to\": 7686}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You can\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t just fly the ball a prescribed number to the hole.\", \"from\": 7708, \"to\": 7770, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the ball\", \"from\": 7729, \"to\": 7737}, {\"ngram\": \"a prescribed number\", \"from\": 7738, \"to\": 7757}, {\"ngram\": \"the hole\", \"from\": 7761, \"to\": 7769}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If you do, it will most likely bounce over the green.\", \"from\": 7771, \"to\": 7824, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the green\", \"from\": 7814, \"to\": 7823}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So either you hit it with an immense level of spin\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094something difficult to do in the wind\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094or you learn to play the bounces.\", \"from\": 7825, \"to\": 7951, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an immense level\", \"from\": 7851, \"to\": 7867}, {\"ngram\": \"the wind\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094or\", \"from\": 7907, \"to\": 7920}, {\"ngram\": \"the bounces\", \"from\": 7939, \"to\": 7950}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Somehow, Schauffele hit 16 of 18 greens in regulation that final day and didn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t make a bogey.\", \"from\": 7952, \"to\": 8047, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Schauffele\", \"from\": 7961, \"to\": 7971}, {\"ngram\": \"18 greens\", \"from\": 7982, \"to\": 7991}, {\"ngram\": \"regulation\", \"from\": 7995, \"to\": 8005}, {\"ngram\": \"a bogey\", \"from\": 8039, \"to\": 8046}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For the less-skilled among us, the ability to run a ball onto a green and not worry about forced carries over water or bunkers makes for a more forgiving experience.\", \"from\": 8049, \"to\": 8214, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 8076, \"to\": 8078}, {\"ngram\": \"the ability\", \"from\": 8080, \"to\": 8091}, {\"ngram\": \"a ball\", \"from\": 8099, \"to\": 8105}, {\"ngram\": \"forced carries\", \"from\": 8139, \"to\": 8153}, {\"ngram\": \"water\", \"from\": 8159, \"to\": 8164}, {\"ngram\": \"bunkers\", \"from\": 8168, \"to\": 8175}, {\"ngram\": \"a more forgiving experience\", \"from\": 8186, \"to\": 8213}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Yes, the pot bunkers are troublesome, so you do your best to play around them.\", \"from\": 8215, \"to\": 8293, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the pot bunkers\", \"from\": 8220, \"to\": 8235}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There is the occasional creek\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094called a burn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094but for the most part, it's more about avoiding tall, wispy rough.\", \"from\": 8294, \"to\": 8408, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a burn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094but\", \"from\": 8333, \"to\": 8345}, {\"ngram\": \"the most part\", \"from\": 8350, \"to\": 8363}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Golf in the U.K. is amazingly accessible, even for visitors, even at otherwise private clubs.\", \"from\": 8410, \"to\": 8503, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8422, \"end\": 8426, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9999999915171429, \"rank\": 5.931943121911154e-09, \"text\": \"U.K.\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Golf\", \"from\": 8410, \"to\": 8414}, {\"ngram\": \"visitors\", \"from\": 8461, \"to\": 8469}, {\"ngram\": \"otherwise private clubs\", \"from\": 8479, \"to\": 8502}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They welcome outsiders because the fees help pay the bills and keep the game affordable to locals and juniors, who pay a pittance in annual dues with nearly unlimited access.\", \"from\": 8504, \"to\": 8678, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"outsiders\", \"from\": 8517, \"to\": 8526}, {\"ngram\": \"the fees\", \"from\": 8535, \"to\": 8543}, {\"ngram\": \"the bills\", \"from\": 8553, \"to\": 8562}, {\"ngram\": \"the game\", \"from\": 8572, \"to\": 8580}, {\"ngram\": \"locals\", \"from\": 8595, \"to\": 8601}, {\"ngram\": \"juniors\", \"from\": 8606, \"to\": 8613}, {\"ngram\": \"a pittance\", \"from\": 8623, \"to\": 8633}, {\"ngram\": \"annual dues\", \"from\": 8637, \"to\": 8648}, {\"ngram\": \"nearly unlimited access\", \"from\": 8654, \"to\": 8677}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Perhaps the best part: even though nearly everyone walks (golf carts, or buggies, are rare), the expectation is that a round will take less than four hours.\", \"from\": 8680, \"to\": 8836, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Perhaps the best part\", \"from\": 8680, \"to\": 8701}, {\"ngram\": \"nearly everyone\", \"from\": 8715, \"to\": 8730}, {\"ngram\": \"golf carts\", \"from\": 8738, \"to\": 8748}, {\"ngram\": \"buggies\", \"from\": 8753, \"to\": 8760}, {\"ngram\": \"the expectation\", \"from\": 8773, \"to\": 8788}, {\"ngram\": \"a round\", \"from\": 8797, \"to\": 8804}, {\"ngram\": \"less than four hours\", \"from\": 8815, \"to\": 8835}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And it usually does.\", \"from\": 8837, \"to\": 8857, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For more information on these courses and many more, check out\\u00c2Scotland: Where Golf Began.\", \"from\": 8859, \"to\": 8949, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"more information\", \"from\": 8863, \"to\": 8879}, {\"ngram\": \"these courses\", \"from\": 8883, \"to\": 8896}, {\"ngram\": \"out\\u00c2Scotland\", \"from\": 8918, \"to\": 8930}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The photos alone are worth your time.\", \"from\": 8950, \"to\": 8987, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The photos\", \"from\": 8950, \"to\": 8960}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After such a strong run in the major championships, Bryson DeChambeau had a disappointing showing at Royal Troon, seemingly attempting to force his long ball approach and scientific methods to a course ill-suited for such a purpose.\", \"from\": 8989, \"to\": 9221, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 9048, \"end\": 9058, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bryson_DeChambeau\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"DeChambeau\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13156709\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bryson_DeChambeau\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bryson_DeChambeau\"}, {\"begin\": 9090, \"end\": 9101, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Royal_Troon_Golf_Club\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Royal Troon\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Royal_Troon_Golf_Club\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Royal_Troon_Golf_Club\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"such a strong run\", \"from\": 8995, \"to\": 9012}, {\"ngram\": \"the major championships\", \"from\": 9016, \"to\": 9039}, {\"ngram\": \"a disappointing showing\", \"from\": 9063, \"to\": 9086}, {\"ngram\": \"his long ball approach\", \"from\": 9133, \"to\": 9155}, {\"ngram\": \"scientific methods\", \"from\": 9160, \"to\": 9178}, {\"ngram\": \"a course\", \"from\": 9182, \"to\": 9190}, {\"ngram\": \"such a purpose\", \"from\": 9206, \"to\": 9220}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He more or less said he would play his game and make it work.\", \"from\": 9223, \"to\": 9284, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his game\", \"from\": 9258, \"to\": 9266}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Although that is likely a bit simplistic, DeChambeau shot 42 over his first nine holes and never recovered, finishing at 9 over for two rounds and missing the cut by two strokes.\", \"from\": 9285, \"to\": 9463, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 9327, \"end\": 9337, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bryson_DeChambeau\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"DeChambeau\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13156709\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bryson_DeChambeau\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bryson_DeChambeau\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his first nine holes\", \"from\": 9351, \"to\": 9371}, {\"ngram\": \"two rounds\", \"from\": 9417, \"to\": 9427}, {\"ngram\": \"the cut\", \"from\": 9440, \"to\": 9447}, {\"ngram\": \"two strokes\", \"from\": 9451, \"to\": 9462}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But DeChambeau, whotied for 11th\\u00c2 at the LIV Golf event in Englandon Sunday, was already talking about making changes for next year\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s Open at Royal Portrush.\", \"from\": 9465, \"to\": 9624, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 9469, \"end\": 9479, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bryson_DeChambeau\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"DeChambeau\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13156709\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bryson_DeChambeau\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bryson_DeChambeau\"}, {\"begin\": 9506, \"end\": 9514, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LIV_Golf\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"LIV Golf\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LIV_Golf\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LIV_Golf\"}, {\"begin\": 9609, \"end\": 9623, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Royal_Portrush_Golf_Club\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Royal Portrush\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Royal_Portrush_Golf_Club\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Royal_Portrush_Golf_Club\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Englandon\", \"from\": 9524, \"to\": 9533}, {\"ngram\": \"changes\", \"from\": 9575, \"to\": 9582}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cFor me, I learned a lot more than I had in the other three majors,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d he said last week.\", \"from\": 9626, \"to\": 9717, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the other three majors\", \"from\": 9672, \"to\": 9694}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cPlaying more of American-style golf, even at Augusta, I have played there enough and I know how to play those types of golf courses for the most part.\", \"from\": 9718, \"to\": 9871, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 9766, \"end\": 9773, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Augusta_Highway\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.256054366952002e-17, \"text\": \"Augusta\", \"types\": [\"Q34442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Augusta_Highway\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Augusta_Highway\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"American-style golf\", \"from\": 9737, \"to\": 9756}, {\"ngram\": \"those types\", \"from\": 9825, \"to\": 9836}, {\"ngram\": \"golf courses\", \"from\": 9840, \"to\": 9852}, {\"ngram\": \"the most part\", \"from\": 9857, \"to\": 9870}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Always can get better in small areas.\", \"from\": 9872, \"to\": 9909, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"small areas\", \"from\": 9897, \"to\": 9908}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cBut the Open Championship has always been kind of a different one for me.\", \"from\": 9911, \"to\": 9987, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Open Championship\", \"from\": 9918, \"to\": 9939}, {\"ngram\": \"kind of a different one\", \"from\": 9956, \"to\": 9979}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I have played well in sunny, dry, normal conditions there, but when it gets really wet and windy and nasty, I have always struggled.\", \"from\": 9988, \"to\": 10120, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"sunny, dry, normal conditions\", \"from\": 10010, \"to\": 10039}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cLast week just felt like I broke the seal a bit in that second round.\", \"from\": 10122, \"to\": 10194, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the seal\", \"from\": 10158, \"to\": 10166}, {\"ngram\": \"that second round\", \"from\": 10176, \"to\": 10193}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Even though I did not play that great, I felt like I could control the golf ball for the first time in those types of conditions, and that was a huge moment for me to go, O.K, I think I can do this if I just work a little bit harder leading into this tournament in these conditions.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d DeChambeau acknowledged the whims of Open weather but also noted how Xander Schauffele managed to handle it the best.\", \"from\": 10195, \"to\": 10599, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 10482, \"end\": 10492, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bryson_DeChambeau\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"DeChambeau\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13156709\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bryson_DeChambeau\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bryson_DeChambeau\"}, {\"begin\": 10551, \"end\": 10568, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Xander_Schauffele\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Xander Schauffele\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13156709\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Xander_Schauffele\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Xander_Schauffele\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the golf ball\", \"from\": 10262, \"to\": 10275}, {\"ngram\": \"the first time\", \"from\": 10280, \"to\": 10294}, {\"ngram\": \"those types\", \"from\": 10298, \"to\": 10309}, {\"ngram\": \"conditions\", \"from\": 10313, \"to\": 10323}, {\"ngram\": \"a huge moment\", \"from\": 10338, \"to\": 10351}, {\"ngram\": \"O.K\", \"from\": 10366, \"to\": 10369}, {\"ngram\": \"this tournament\", \"from\": 10441, \"to\": 10456}, {\"ngram\": \"the whims\", \"from\": 10505, \"to\": 10514}, {\"ngram\": \"Open weather\", \"from\": 10518, \"to\": 10530}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cYou always have to have luck on your side in certain conditions, but playing really steady golf like Xander did showed that it does not matter; you can win with just a consistent good game,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d he said.\", \"from\": 10601, \"to\": 10805, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 10705, \"end\": 10711, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Xander_Schauffele\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.36845728169705e-58, \"text\": \"Xander\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13156709\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Xander_Schauffele\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Xander_Schauffele\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cYou\", \"from\": 10601, \"to\": 10607}, {\"ngram\": \"luck\", \"from\": 10628, \"to\": 10632}, {\"ngram\": \"your side\", \"from\": 10636, \"to\": 10645}, {\"ngram\": \"certain conditions\", \"from\": 10649, \"to\": 10667}, {\"ngram\": \"really steady golf\", \"from\": 10681, \"to\": 10699}, {\"ngram\": \"just a consistent good game\", \"from\": 10765, \"to\": 10792}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cHe obviously conquered that challenge, and one that I am looking forward to next year.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d>The Olympics comes with perks, some more important than others.\", \"from\": 10806, \"to\": 10962, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cHe\", \"from\": 10806, \"to\": 10811}, {\"ngram\": \"that challenge\", \"from\": 10832, \"to\": 10846}, {\"ngram\": \"next year.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d>The Olympics\", \"from\": 10885, \"to\": 10911}, {\"ngram\": \"perks\", \"from\": 10923, \"to\": 10928}, {\"ngram\": \"others\", \"from\": 10955, \"to\": 10961}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In a pro game that is now paying upwards of $3 million to major championship winners, the men\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s player who wins Olympic gold will get $50,000.\", \"from\": 10963, \"to\": 11107, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a pro game\", \"from\": 10966, \"to\": 10976}, {\"ngram\": \"major championship winners\", \"from\": 11021, \"to\": 11047}, {\"ngram\": \"the men\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s player\", \"from\": 11049, \"to\": 11067}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic gold\", \"from\": 11077, \"to\": 11089}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Various Olympic organizing committees also give payments to medalists.\", \"from\": 11108, \"to\": 11178, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Various Olympic organizing committees\", \"from\": 11108, \"to\": 11145}, {\"ngram\": \"payments\", \"from\": 11156, \"to\": 11164}, {\"ngram\": \"medalists\", \"from\": 11168, \"to\": 11177}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the case of the U.S., it is $37,500 for gold, $22,250 for silver and $15,000 for bronze.>Clearly the biggest perk is a spot in the major championships.\", \"from\": 11179, \"to\": 11333, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the case\", \"from\": 11182, \"to\": 11190}, {\"ngram\": \"the U.S.\", \"from\": 11194, \"to\": 11202}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 11222, \"to\": 11226}, {\"ngram\": \"silver\", \"from\": 11240, \"to\": 11246}, {\"ngram\": \"bronze.>Clearly\", \"from\": 11263, \"to\": 11278}, {\"ngram\": \"the biggest perk\", \"from\": 11279, \"to\": 11295}, {\"ngram\": \"a spot\", \"from\": 11299, \"to\": 11305}, {\"ngram\": \"the major championships\", \"from\": 11309, \"to\": 11332}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s not a concern for the likes ofXander SchauffeleandScottie Scheffler, but it is for Mexico\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099sCarlos Ortiz, who plays for LIV Golf.\", \"from\": 11334, \"to\": 11473, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 11401, \"end\": 11410, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scottie_Scheffler\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4722492538179417e-81, \"text\": \"Scheffler\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13156709\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scottie_Scheffler\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scottie_Scheffler\"}, {\"begin\": 11443, \"end\": 11448, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tito_Ortiz\", \"score\": 0.9999999999972715, \"rank\": 2.349069826515293e-12, \"text\": \"Ortiz\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tito_Ortiz\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tito_Ortiz\"}, {\"begin\": 11464, \"end\": 11472, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LIV_Golf\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"LIV Golf\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LIV_Golf\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LIV_Golf\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"That\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s not a concern\", \"from\": 11334, \"to\": 11356}, {\"ngram\": \"the likes\", \"from\": 11361, \"to\": 11370}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A gold medal means spots in all four major championships next year.>A victory also means a spot in the Players Championship (for now, provided you are not playing for LIV Golf) and a spot in the season-opening Sentry if you are a PGA Tour member.\", \"from\": 11474, \"to\": 11720, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 11641, \"end\": 11649, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LIV_Golf\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"LIV Golf\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LIV_Golf\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LIV_Golf\"}, {\"begin\": 11704, \"end\": 11712, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/PGA_Tour\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.969805026729117e-46, \"text\": \"PGA Tour\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/PGA_Tour\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/PGA_Tour\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A gold medal\", \"from\": 11474, \"to\": 11486}, {\"ngram\": \"spots\", \"from\": 11493, \"to\": 11498}, {\"ngram\": \"all four major championships\", \"from\": 11502, \"to\": 11530}, {\"ngram\": \"next year.>A victory\", \"from\": 11531, \"to\": 11551}, {\"ngram\": \"a spot\", \"from\": 11563, \"to\": 11569}, {\"ngram\": \"the Players Championship\", \"from\": 11573, \"to\": 11597}, {\"ngram\": \"the season-opening Sentry\", \"from\": 11665, \"to\": 11690}]}, {\"sentence\": \">Not to be forgotten: Official World Golf Ranking points.\", \"from\": 11722, \"to\": 11779, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \">Not to be forgotten: Official World Golf Ranking points\", \"from\": 11722, \"to\": 11778}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That will be determined once the tournament is underway, but in 2021 Schauffele received 50 points for winning.\", \"from\": 11780, \"to\": 11891, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the tournament\", \"from\": 11809, \"to\": 11823}, {\"ngram\": \"Schauffele\", \"from\": 11849, \"to\": 11859}, {\"ngram\": \"50 points\", \"from\": 11869, \"to\": 11878}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That is half of what you get for winning a major but it\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s in line with regular PGA Tour events\\u00e